      <title>环球音乐成立新品牌部门进军中国市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/universal-music-extends-push-into-china-with-new-label-division</link>
      <description><![CDATA[环球音乐集团（Universal Music Group NV）已在香港周边的粤港澳大湾区设立了唱片部门，让这家全球最大的音乐公司在中国南部获得了更大的立足点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/universal-music-extends-push-into-china-with-new-label-division</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 09:43:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国对 Calvin Klein 母公司涉嫌抵制新疆展开调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/china-probes-calvin-klein-parent-over-suspected-xinjiang-boycott</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国表示，将对美国服装制造商 PVH 公司因涉嫌抵制来自新疆地区的棉花进行调查，此项调查可能会导致 Tommy Hilfiger 和 Calvin Klein 的母公司受到处罚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/china-probes-calvin-klein-parent-over-suspected-xinjiang-boycott</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 09:40:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国股市交易员担心政策推动的涨势可能只是昙花一现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/china-stock-traders-worry-policy-fueled-gains-may-be-shortlived</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，中国股市创下四年多来最大涨幅，此前中国政府推出了最新一轮刺激计划。但很少有人认为这种好运会持续下去。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/china-stock-traders-worry-policy-fueled-gains-may-be-shortlived</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 09:38:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
